OL,3,CFour arrested following fatal stabbing
OL,4,Cin Peckham
OL,6,FOfficers investigating the fatal
OL,7,Fstabbing of a man have arrested four
OL,8,Fpeople on suspicion of murder.
OL,10,FThe Met was called at 03:54hrs on
OL,11,FMonday, 6 April to reports of
OL,12,Fdisturbance involving a group of
OL,13,Fpeople outside a nightclub in Ruby
OL,14,FStreet.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
