OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775574665
OL,3,CFour arrested following fatal stabbing
OL,4,Cin Peckham
OL,6,FUpon arrival, officers and paramedics
OL,7,Ffrom the London Ambulance Service
OL,8,Ffound a 26-year-old man with stab
OL,9,Fwounds. Despite the efforts of
OL,10,Femergency services, the man died at
OL,11,Fthe scene. His next-of-kin have been
OL,12,Finformed and are being supported by
OL,13,Fspecialist officers.
OL,15,FTwo other men in their 20s were also
OL,16,Ffound injured at the scene. They both
OL,17,Fremain in hospital in a life-
OL,18,Fthreatening condition.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775574665
OL,3,CFour arrested following fatal stabbing
OL,4,Cin Peckham
OL,6,FFour men, one aged 18 and three aged
OL,7,F24, were arrested later on Monday, 6
OL,8,FApril on suspicion of murder. They all
OL,9,Fremain in custody.
OL,11,FDetective Chief Inspector Neil John,
OL,12,Fwho is leading the Met's
OL,13,Finvestigation, said:
OL,15,F"This is a deeply tragic incident, and
OL,16,Four thoughts are with the victim's
OL,17,Ffamily during this difficult time.
OL,19,F"We have already arrested four men and
OL,20,Four investigation continues at pace.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775574665
OL,3,CFour arrested following fatal stabbing
OL,4,Cin Peckham
OL,6,F"We are aware of the concern that this
OL,7,Fwill cause the local community and
OL,8,Fthose in the area will notice an
OL,9,Fincreased police presence throughout
OL,10,Fthe day.
OL,12,F"This assault occurred outside a busy
OL,13,Fnightclub, and we'd encourage anyone
OL,14,Fwho has any information, dashcam or
OL,15,Fmobile phone footage which could
OL,16,Fsupport the investigation to contact
OL,17,Fus."
